title: SleepPhones (Official Video)
description:
Answers to your questions: 

What are SleepPhones?
How do SleepPhones work?
How do you use SleepPhones?
How do I buy SleepPhones?

SleepPhones are the most comfortable headphones for relaxing to music, drowning out snoring and loud neighbors, SleepPhones work with iPod and most music players. Like soft pajamas for your ears, SleepPhones let you listen to anything in bed without disturbing others.
